title: I'm Really Hurt
lyrics: eotteohke jakku nunmuli na neo ttaemune naega neomu apa keureohke neoman saenggakhamyeon deo wae jakkuman ni hyanggiga namyeon tto nan ni sajineul bomyeon tto nan ni saenggake oneuldo nan neomu a a a a pa(wa) naega a a a apa(wa) imankkeum apeul georan geol nan jeongmal jeongmal mollas seo jeongmal a a a apa(wa) maeumi a a a apa(wa) ireohke bogo sipeul georan geol jeongmal jeongmal mollas seo neomu a pa ireohke nal tteonaji ma jebal keuman nal apeuge haji ma
